{{Vgname|变形|en=Proteus}}是埃德·凯与戴维·卡纳加设计和制作的2013年[[冒险游戏|探险]]步行模拟器电子游戏，支持[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]、[[MacOS|OS X]]、[[Linux|Linux]]、[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]和[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]平台。玩家在游戏[[程序化生成|程序化生成]]的环境穿梭但没有既定目标，游戏世界的动植物散发独特音乐特征，这些特征相互结合，促使游戏音频根据玩家周边环境动态变化。

游戏2008年开始开发，凯的初步构想类似《[[上古卷轴IV：湮没|上古卷轴IV：湮没]]》，是开放式结局的[[角色扮演游戏|角色扮演游戏]]，但因工作量太大改按“非传统非暴力”项目重新设计。音效设计师兼作曲家戴维·卡纳加2010年加入开发，PlayStation 3家用游戏机与PlayStation Vita掌上游戏机版本由[[曲线数据|曲线公司]]开发，开发组还应[[索尼|索尼]]要求为PlayStation Vita版增加新游戏功能。

《变形》获2011年[[IndieCade|IndieCade]]最佳音效奖，另有2012年[[独立游戏节|独立游戏节]]新品奖提名。游戏获评论界好评，并以音频功能最受青睐，但也有文章批评游戏过于简单，[[重玩價值|重玩价值]]有限。许多评论以本作为例探讨电子游戏是否属于艺术形式，还有评论质疑《变形》到底算不算电子游戏。

== 游戏玩法 ==
[[File:Memorial_in_Proteus.png|thumb]]

玩家启动《变形》后以[[第一人称视角游戏|第一人称视角]]探索[[像素画|像素画]]风格岛屿，上有山丘、树木、建筑，还有青蛙、兔子等动物，每次启动游戏这些元素都[[程序化生成|不一样]]<ref>{{cite web | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225130845/https://kotaku.com/a-gorgeous-digital-world-that-you-can-explore-starting-5980379 | url = https://kotaku.com/a-gorgeous-digital-world-that-you-can-explore-starting-5980379 | title = A Gorgeous Digital World That You Can Explore Starting Today | date = 2013-01-30 | work = [[Kotaku|Kotaku]] | first = Patricia | last = Hernandez | access-date = 2021-03-14 | publisher = Gawker Media | archive-date = 2021-02-25 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/ambient-works-proteus-ep | title = Ambient Works: Proteus EP | date = 2011-06-12 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | first = Jim | last = Rossignol | work = [[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]] | archive-date = 2021-02-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210227085439/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/ambient-works-proteus-ep | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="EuroG">{{cite web | url = https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-02-05-proteus-review | title = Proteus review | date = 2013-02-05 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | first = Oli | last = Welsh | work = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] | publisher = Gamer Network | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225140058/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-02-05-proteus-review }}</ref>。游戏的重点是探索而非互动，其中没有情节，也没有向玩家提供任何指示<ref name="GSpot">{{cite web | url = https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/proteus-review/1900-6403756/ | date = 2013-02-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210226210049/https://www.gamespot.com/reviews/proteus-review/1900-6403756/ | access-date = 2021-03-14 | first = John | last = Robertson | work = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | title = Proteus Review | publisher = [[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]] | archive-date = 2021-02-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。可能发生互动的情况都很少，比如玩家靠近时动物可能逃开<ref>{{cite web | work = Rock, Paper, Shotgun | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225033851/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/the-hills-are-alive-proteus-beta-release | url = https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/the-hills-are-alive-proteus-beta-release | title = The Hills Are Alive: Proteus Beta Release | date = 2012-02-27 | first = Adam | last = Smith | access-date = 2021-03-14 | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。游戏背景音效根据动作和位置不断变化，站在山顶时可能寂静无声，下山时声音可能变得非常密集。玩家靠近动物及其他物体时，背景音效还会叠加其他声音和音符。<ref name="IGN">{{cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308013503/https://www.ign.com/articles/2013/02/09/proteus-review | dead-url = no | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2013/02/09/proteus-review | title = Proteus Review - A Virtual Vacation In More Ways Than One. | date = 2013-02-08 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | first = Nathan | last = Grayson | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | publisher = Ziff Davis | archive-date = 2021-03-08 }}</ref>岛上许多物体是用[[二维计算机图形|二维]][[精灵图|精灵图]]渲染，与三维风景对比显著<ref name=":3">{{Cite news | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308164301/https://www.pressreader.com/australia/edge/20161208/283304637132749 | url = https://www.pressreader.com/australia/edge/20161208/283304637132749 | title = The Making Of... | last = Gordon | first = Lewis | date = 2016-12-08 | work = [[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]] | access-date = 2021-03-14 }}</ref>。

玩家开始游戏后先要漂洋过海抵达岛屿<ref name="IGN" />，然后在岛上自由活动。这里起初是春季，玩家可以夜间到指定区域调整时间进入其他季节并继续探索，游戏最后随冬季结束完结。岛上风景随季节变化，例如树木会在秋天落叶。<ref name="EuroG" /><ref>{{cite web | last = Walker | work = Rock, Paper, Shotgun | url = https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/proteus-review | title = Wot I Think: Proteus | date = 2013-01-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201111232052/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2013/01/30/proteus-review/ | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2020-11-11 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | first = John }}</ref>玩家可以用“保存[[明信片|明信片]]”功能截图，该功能还可用于存档<ref name="EuroG" />。

除基本游戏元素外，[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]版玩家还能用后置触摸屏直接影响岛屿环境，并根据当前日期和在真实世界的位置生成岛屿<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Gamer Network | first = Jeffrey | last = Matulef | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112005124/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-10-23-proteus-rolls-onto-ps3-and-vita-next-week | url = https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-10-23-proteus-rolls-onto-ps3-and-vita-next-week | title = Proteus rolls onto PS3 and Vita next week | date = 2013-10-29 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | work = Eurogamer | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | archive-date = 2015-06-11 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.engadget.com/2013-10-10-proteus-launching-on-ps3-and-vita-this-month-with-new-world-gene.html | title = Proteus launching on PS3 and Vita this month with new world generation options | first = Mike | last = Suszek | date = 2013-10-10 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | work = [[Joystiq|Joystiq]] | publisher = [[美国在线|AOL]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150611220807/http://www.engadget.com/2013/10/10/proteus-launching-on-ps3-and-vita-this-month-with-new-world-gene/ }}</ref>。

== 开发 ==
[[File:Autumn_in_Proteus.png|thumb]]

英国游戏设计师埃德·凯2008年开始在夜间和周末设计《变形》，但2010年戴维·卡纳加参加开发时游戏形式都没敲定<ref name="Gama">{{cite web | publisher = UBM TechWeb | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210224231848/https://gamasutra.com/view/news/39419/Road_to_the_IGF_Key_and_Kanagas_Proteus.php | url = https://gamasutra.com/view/news/39419/Road_to_the_IGF_Key_and_Kanagas_Proteus.php | title = Road to the IGF: Key and Kanaga's Proteus | date = 2012-01-27 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | first = Leigh | last = Alexander | work = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-date = 2021-02-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="interview">{{cite web | url = https://www.pcworld.com/article/251236/one_on_one_with_proteus_developer_ed_key.html | archive-date = 2021-03-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210309063825/https://www.pcworld.com/article/251236/one_on_one_with_proteus_developer_ed_key.html | title = One-on-One With Proteus Developer Ed Key | date = 2012-03-04 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | work = [[个人电脑世界|PC World]] | first = Zohra | last = Ashpari | publisher = [[国际数据集团|IDG]] | dead-url = no }}</ref>。凯的初步设想类似《[[上古卷轴IV：湮没|上古卷轴IV：湮没]]》，属程序化[[角色扮演游戏|角色扮演游戏]]，玩家探索城镇并完成任务。但这样的游戏设计工作量极大，开发人员决定改按“非传统非暴力”项目重来<ref name="RPSinterview">{{cite web | url = https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/staying-humble-proteus-origins-and-ed-keys-next-game#more-157738 | title = Staying Humble: Proteus' Origins And Ed Key's Next Game | date = 2013-06-26 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | first = Nathan | last = Grayson | work = Rock, Paper, Shotgun | archive-date = 2021-02-24 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210224172942/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/staying-humble-proteus-origins-and-ed-keys-next-game#more-157738 }}</ref>。游戏开发的第一项技术是景观生成器，源自凯在英格兰[[威爾特郡|威爾特郡]][[埃夫伯里_(威尔特郡)|埃夫伯里]]乡间行走时产生的灵感。确定开发探险游戏后，凯为尝试各种游戏理念反复变更《变形》的发展方向。<ref name=":3" />

凯用[[C♯|C#]]编程语言编写的[[游戏引擎|游戏引擎]]开发《变形》<ref name=":4">{{cite web | archive-date = 2014-12-26 | access-date = 2014-12-26 | url = http://www.visitproteus.com/forum/index.php?topic=164.0 | title = Proteus Engine | date = 2013-01-31 | work = Proteus Forum | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141226200447/http://www.visitproteus.com/forum/index.php?topic=164.0 }}</ref>。他在开发早期就确认游戏视觉风格，很早就确定采用[[印象派|印象派]]风格树木；[[装饰风艺术|装饰风艺术]]和[[保罗·纳什|保罗·纳什]]的作品对游戏影响很大<ref name=":3" />。卡纳加以音频作曲的身份加入后，开发组测试各种构想完善游戏的音乐和音效机制，一度让玩家可以在游戏中自创音乐，但凯和卡纳加觉得这会分散玩家注意力，把注重探索的游戏变成创意工具，最后取消自定义音乐和音效功能<ref>{{cite web | url = https://indiegamesplus.com/2012/10/video_how_abstraction_gave_pro | title = Video: How Abstraction Gave Proteus its Voice | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-03-14 | archive-date = 2021-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210305031010/https://indiegamesplus.com/2012/10/video_how_abstraction_gave_pro | date = 2012-10-13 | work = [[Gamasutra|IndieGames.com]] | publisher = UBM plc }}</ref>。游戏开发期间和发行后，开发组都曾表示有意让玩家创建[[遊戲模組|遊戲模組]]，游戏社区后来也的确有这类模组诞生<ref name="interview" /><ref name=":4" /><ref>{{cite web | work = [[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]] | publisher = Future plc | access-date = 2021-03-14 | url = https://www.pcgamer.com/purgateus-is-a-dark-remixmod-for-proteus-and-it-looks-fantastic/ | title = Purgateus is a dark remix/mod for Proteus, and it looks fantastic | last = Sykes | first = Tom | date = 2014-05-26 | archive-date = 2021-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210304201100/https://www.pcgamer.com/purgateus-is-a-dark-remixmod-for-proteus-and-it-looks-fantastic/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2013年1月30日，《变形》发布[[Microsoft_Windows|Windows]]和[[MacOS|OS X]]平台版，同年4月8日发布[[Linux|Linux]]版<ref name="PC">{{Cite web | url = https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/proteus-gets-a-releaseus-dateus-at-lasteus | title = Proteus Gets A Releaseus Dateus At Lasteus | date = 2013-01-21 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | first = Alec | last = Meer | work = Rock, Paper, Shotgun | archive-date = 2021-02-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210224235450/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/proteus-gets-a-releaseus-dateus-at-lasteus | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Linux">{{cite web | archive-date = 2015-10-22 | website = Visit Proteus | url = http://www.visitproteus.com/version-1-1-now-available-linux-steam-big-picture-support/ | title = Version 1.1 now available: Linux, Steam Big Picture support | date = 2013-04-09 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151022231300/http://www.visitproteus.com/version-1-1-now-available-linux-steam-big-picture-support/ | access-date = 2021-03-14 | first = Ed | last = Key }}</ref>。2012年开始预订时还提供“神器版”，盒装游戏副本还提供图画、音频，以及游戏开发笔记<ref>{{cite web | last = O'Connor | publisher = Gamerhub | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225121853/https://www.shacknews.com/article/72614/proteus-pre-orders-pack-playable-beta | url = https://www.shacknews.com/article/72614/proteus-pre-orders-pack-playable-beta | title = Proteus pre-orders pack playable beta | date = 2012-02-27 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | work = Shacknews | first = Alice | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-02-25 }}</ref>。但神器版2013年底还没发货，凯亲自向玩家道歉并承诺向提出的玩家退款<ref>{{cite web | last = Mejia | work = Shacknews | publisher = Gamerhub | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210224211618/https://www.shacknews.com/article/82293/proteus-12-patch-on-pcmaclinux-adds-ps3vita-wild-islands | title = Proteus PC patch adds PlayStation's Wild Islands | date = 2013-12-10 | dead-url = no | url = https://www.shacknews.com/article/82293/proteus-12-patch-on-pcmaclinux-adds-ps3vita-wild-islands | first = Ozzie | archive-date = 2021-02-24 | access-date = 2021-03-14 }}</ref>。2016年7月，神器版终于开售<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://twitter.com/atwistedtree/status/752860619573981185 | title = Twisted Tree Games | date = 2016-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200922014653/https://twitter.com/atwistedtree/status/752860619573981185 | publisher = [[Twitter|Twitter]] | access-date = 2021-03-14 | archive-date = 2020-09-22 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

曲线公司在游戏发布前后主动联系开发商，提议把《变形》[[移植_(軟體)|移植]]到[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]和[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]平台<ref>{{cite news | first = Keith | newspaper = The Guardian | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308225823/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2013/nov/01/proteus-games-playstation-3-vita | url = https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2013/nov/01/proteus-games-playstation-3-vita | title = Proteus: adventure game is a meditation on place and nature | date = 2013-11-01 | last = Stuart | dead-url = no | access-date = 2021-03-14 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.edge-online.com/news/curve-studios-is-bringing-proteus-to-ps3-and-vita/ | title = Curve Studios is bringing Proteus to PS3 and Vita | date = 2013-07-01 | access-date = 2014-12-26 | work = Edge | publisher = Future plc | first = Neil | last = Long | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141226193551/http://www.edge-online.com/news/curve-studios-is-bringing-proteus-to-ps3-and-vita/ | archive-date = 2014-12-26 }}</ref>，这两个版本均采用该司自有的游戏引擎<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.shacknews.com/article/81544/proteus-creator-explains-ps3-vita-exclusive-features | title = Proteus creator explains PS3/Vita-exclusive features | date = 2013-10-11 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | work = Shacknews | publisher = Gamerhub | first = Ozzie | last = Mejia | archive-date = 2021-01-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210116174142/https://www.shacknews.com/article/81544/proteus-creator-explains-ps3-vita-exclusive-features | dead-url = no }}</ref>。索尼要求增加游戏功能，但凯表示，索尼始终没有要求为这些功能变更开发方向，他为游戏加入以玩家地点和日期为基础的世界生成器，玩家能用PlayStation Vita的后置触摸屏改变游戏世界色彩<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1">{{cite web | archive-date = 2021-02-26 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210226001135/https://www.pocketgamer.com/articles/055055/proteus/ | url = https://www.pocketgamer.com/articles/055055/proteus/ | title = Proteus review - PlayStation Vita reviews | date = 2013-11-07 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | first = Mike | last = Rose | work = Pocket Gamer | publisher = Steel Media }}</ref>。他还称，游戏未来可能推出新版本，增加根据玩家地点和日期生成世界的功能<ref name=":0">{{cite web | publisher = [[赫斯特国际集团|Hearst Magazines UK]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210302202137/https://www.digitalspy.com/videogames/a530326/proteus-how-the-exploration-game-came-to-playstation-platform/ | archive-date = 2021-03-02 | dead-url = no | last = Reynolds | url = https://www.digitalspy.com/videogames/a530326/proteus-how-the-exploration-game-came-to-playstation-platform/ | title = 'Proteus': How the exploration game came to PlayStation platform | date = 2013-11-13 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | first = Matthew | work = [[數碼間諜|Digital Spy]] }}</ref>。2013年10月29日，PlayStation 3和PlayStation Vita版发布<ref name="PlayStation release">{{cite web | access-date = 2021-03-14 | publisher = [[索尼|Sony]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210227112645/https://blog.playstation.com/2013/10/29/proteus-out-today-on-ps3-and-ps-vita/ | url = https://blog.playstation.com/2013/10/29/proteus-out-today-on-ps3-and-ps-vita/ | title = Proteus Out Today on PS3 and PS Vita | last = Clarke | first = Rob | work = PlayStation.Blog | date = 2013-10-29 | archive-date = 2021-02-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

