=== 发行前 ===
游戏正式发行前就在许多[[独立游戏|独立游戏]]节提供[[軟件版本週期|测试版]]，引起电子游戏媒体关注。《变形》获2011年IndieCade奖最佳音效奖，<ref name="best audio" />另有2012年游戏城市奖提名，但最后获奖的是《[[风之旅人|风之旅人]]》<ref>{{cite web | newspaper = The Guardian | first = Keith | last = Stuart | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308174842/https://www.theguardian.com/technology/gamesblog/2012/oct/04/gamecity-prize-shortlist-announced | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no | date = 2012-10-04 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | url = https://www.theguardian.com/technology/gamesblog/2012/oct/04/gamecity-prize-shortlist-announced | title = GameCity prize 2012 – shortlist announced }}</ref>。《变形》获2012年[[独立游戏节|独立游戏节]]新品奖提名，该奖旨在鼓励抽象和非常规游戏开发；游戏还因音效表现获[[谢默斯·麦克纳利大奖|谢默斯·麦克纳利大奖]]特别表彰<ref name="Gama" /><ref>{{cite web | access-date = 2021-03-14 | work = Rock, Paper, Shotgun | url = https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/they-could-be-heroes-igf-2012-finalists | title = They Could Be Heroes: IGF 2012 Finalists | date = 2012-01-10 | first = Alec | last = Meer | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225073834/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/they-could-be-heroes-igf-2012-finalists }}</ref>。《变形》获2012年“A MAZE.”独立游戏节最神奇独立游戏奖，同年收入[[現代藝術博物館|現代藝術博物館]]“常识”展区<ref name="best audio" /><ref name="A MAZE" /><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.visitproteus.com/proteus-moma/ | title = Proteus @ MoMA | work = Proteus | author = David | date = 2013-01-21 | access-date = 2015-04-21 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150421133710/http://www.visitproteus.com/proteus-moma/ | archive-date = 2015-04-21 }}</ref>。

吉姆·罗西格诺尔在《[[Rock,_Paper,_Shotgun|Rock, Paper, Shotgun]]》发文探讨2011年的[[冒险游戏|探险游戏]]时称赞《变形》魅力十足，在他接触过的独自游戏中名列前茅<ref>{{cite web | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112030718/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2011/11/24/is-2011-the-year-of-game-world-exploration/ | url = https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/is-2011-the-year-of-game-world-exploration | title = Is 2011 The Year Of Game World Exploration? | date = 2011-11-24 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | first = Jim | last = Rossignol | work = Rock, Paper, Shotgun | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]的文章认为游戏令人沉醉，独特且耐人寻味，以致作者都连玩好多遍<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Ziff Davis | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308204328/https://www.ign.com/articles/2012/04/17/proteus-stimulates-your-wanderlust | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2012/04/17/proteus-stimulates-your-wanderlust | title = Proteus Stimulates Your Wanderlust | date = 2012-04-17 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | first = Rick | last = Lane | work = IGN | dead-url = no | archive-date = 2021-03-08 }}</ref>。[[PC_Gamer|PC Gamer]]也对《变形》青眼有加，特别认可游戏持续变化的音乐和音效，以及根据玩家一举一动反应的变化形式<ref>{{cite web | work = PC Gamer | publisher = Future plc | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225085613/https://www.pcgamer.com/proteus-the-best-song-ive-ever-played/ | url = https://www.pcgamer.com/proteus-the-best-song-ive-ever-played/ | title = Proteus: the best song I've ever played | date = 2012-03-30 | access-date = 2021-03-14 | first = Tom | last = Francis | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 发行后 ===
《变形》发行后同样普受好评，Windows版在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]和[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]统计的好评度分别达八成和七成七<ref name= "GR">{{cite web | url = http://www.gamerankings.com/pc/656779-proteus/index.html | title = Proteus for PC | access-date = 2019-06-06 | work = [[GameRankings|GameRankings]] | archive-date = 2019-06-06 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190606131315/http://www.gamerankings.com/pc/656779-proteus/index.html }}</ref><ref name="MC" />。[[Shacknews|Shacknews]]网站开展的民调结果把《变形》排在2013年最佳游戏第七名，称赞游戏没有任何复杂的情节和解释，令人身心放松<ref>{{cite web | publisher = Gamerhub | access-date = 2021-03-15 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210224151923/https://www.shacknews.com/article/82701/best-of-2013-7-proteus | url = https://www.shacknews.com/article/82701/best-of-2013-7-proteus | title = Best of 2013: #7 - Proteus | last = O'Connor | first = Alice | date = 2014-01-17 | work = Shacknews | archive-date = 2021-02-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

评论员赞扬游戏的动态音效，对游戏体验颇为满意。帕特里克·汉考克在[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]网站发文，认为本作“最大的成就”便是动态音效和音乐，自称探索过所有物体来弄清游戏在音频上到底有多大建树。<ref name="Destructoid" />IGN网站称“只是到处走走就有（声音）充满周围，这种感觉意外迷人”，正是这种探索每种动物和物体声音的过程令人无比享受<ref name="IGN" />。PC Gamer网站同样高度评价游戏密集的音频编排<ref name="EuroG" /><ref name="PCGUS" />。《[[Edge_(杂志)|Edge]]》杂志对游戏音频整体满意，只是感染力尚嫌不足，特别是在大部分季节音乐缺乏鼓点伴奏的情况下<ref name="Edge" />。

评论员对游戏多样化和[[重玩價值|重玩價值]]方面评价不一。IGN认为《变形》值得重玩，每次通关都能带给玩家更深层的感受。<ref name="IGN" />[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]感觉每次生成的岛屿虽说内容不尽相同，但进入游戏后期时依然颇为相似，所以不像前期好玩<ref name="GSpot" />。PC Gamer也有类似看法，觉得游戏快结束时玩家已经没什么可以探索，进而感觉无聊，末期岛上动物很少更令情况加重<ref name="PCGUS" />。

PlayStation 3与PlayStation Vita版同样普受好评<ref>{{cite web | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225074011/http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-3/proteus | url = https://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-3/proteus | title = Proteus for PlayStation 3 reviews | access-date = 2021-03-15 | work = Metacritic | publisher = CBS Interactive }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | access-date = 2021-03-15 | url = https://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-vita/proteus | title = Proteus for PlayStation Vita reviews | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210224185542/https://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-vita/proteus | dead-url = no | work = Metacritic | publisher = CBS Interactive | archive-date = 2021-02-24 }}</ref>。[[Pocket_Gamer|Pocket Gamer]]称赞游戏音频和PlayStation Vita版的PlayStation獎盃等额外功能，令玩家乐意重玩。文章指出游戏在性能表现上尚有不足，特别是在移动摄像机时。<ref name=":1" />《[[地铁报_(英国)|地铁报]]》发文赞扬游戏“迷人的互动体验”，特别是互动产生的音乐<ref>{{cite web | archive-date = 2021-02-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210224133034/https://metro.co.uk/2013/11/04/proteus-psn-review-a-new-journey-4172940/ | url = https://metro.co.uk/2013/11/04/proteus-psn-review-a-new-journey-4172940/ | title = Proteus PSN review – a new journey | date = 2013-11-04 | access-date = 2021-03-15 | work = Metro | publisher = DMG Media | first = Roger | last = Hargreaves | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《[[PlayStation官方杂志－英国|PlayStation官方杂志]]》声称《变形》PlayStation 3版“简单但效果极佳”，称赞游戏非常独特而神奇<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.officialplaystationmagazine.co.uk/review/proteus-ps3-review-official-playstation-magazine-score/ | title = Proteus PS3 review: A walk to remember | access-date = 2014-12-30 | date = 2013-10-29 | first = Joel | last = Gregory | work = [[PlayStation官方杂志－英国|PlayStation Official Magazine]] | publisher = [[未來出版社|Future Publishing]] | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141230000244/http://www.officialplaystationmagazine.co.uk/review/proteus-ps3-review-official-playstation-magazine-score/ | archive-date = 2014-12-30 }}</ref>。

玩家和新闻工作者对《变形》是否算[[电子游戏|电子游戏]]看法不一，反方主要论点在于游戏缺乏目的或目标<ref name="Gamasutra game">{{cite web | url = https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/185645/ | title = Is Proteus a game -- and if not, who cares? | date = 2013-01-30 | access-date = 2021-03-15 | first = Mike | last = Rose | work = Gamasutra | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225235611/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/185645/ | publisher = UBM TechWeb | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | archive-date = 2014-11-29 | url = http://www.edge-online.com/features/what-does-it-mean-to-be-a-game/ | title = What does it mean to be a game? | date = 2013-05-17 | access-date = 2014-11-29 | work = Edge | publisher = Future plc | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141129133357/http://www.edge-online.com/features/what-does-it-mean-to-be-a-game/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.vg247.com/2013/02/27/proteus-homesick-for-unfamiliar-places/ | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210225013208/https://www.vg247.com/2013/02/27/proteus-homesick-for-unfamiliar-places/ | title = Proteus: homesick for unfamiliar places | date = 2013-02-27 | access-date = 2021-03-15 | work = [[VG247|VG247]] | archive-date = 2021-02-25 | dead-url = no | first = Brenna | last = Hillier }}</ref>。《变形》开发人员和部分媒体声称本作属于“[[反游戏|反游戏]]”引发争议<ref>{{cite web | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210304131407/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/185885/Opinion_Its_totally_OK_to_not_like_antigames.php | title = Opinion: It's totally OK to not like 'anti-games' | date = 2013-02-01 | url = https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/185885/Opinion_Its_totally_OK_to_not_like_antigames.php | first = Mike | last = Rose | access-date = 2021-03-15 | work = Gamasutra | publisher = UBM TechWeb | archive-date = 2021-03-04 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | title = Proteus developer responds to 'anti-game' labels | last = Farokhmanesh | url = https://www.polygon.com/2013/2/3/3947754/proteus-developer-responds-to-anti-game-labels | first = Megan | date = 2013-02-03 | work = [[Polygon|Polygon]] | access-date = 2021-03-15 | archive-date = 2021-03-08 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210308124926/https://www.polygon.com/2013/2/3/3947754/proteus-developer-responds-to-anti-game-labels }}</ref>。[[伊恩·波格斯特|伊恩·波格斯特]]指出，本作有意避免朝传统方向设计，在他看来，《变形》无疑是游戏，只不过不是为玩家而游戏，而是让玩家感受岛屿的游戏<ref>{{Cite book | title = How to Talk about Videogames | last = Bogost | first = Ian | publisher = University of Minnesota Press | year = 2015 | isbn = 978-1452949871}}</ref>。IGN认为，本作有行为（岛上行走）也有目标（探索、感受四季），所以是游戏<ref name="IGN" />。《Edge》杂志主张，游戏包含日夜交替、天气变化，还有玩家触发的季度变化，这都令《变形》符合游戏的各项标准<ref name="Edge" />。埃德·凯指出，《变形》包含基本游戏机制，玩家可以自行选择是否触发，而且触发后不一定会有反应。但他主张不要严格定义什么是游戏，否则只会助长保守和防备心理。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://kotaku.com/proteus-creator-defends-his-game-as-a-game-5981097 | title = Proteus' Creator Defends His Game—as a Game | date = 2013-02-02 | access-date = 2021-03-15 | first = Owen | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210303211755/https://kotaku.com/proteus-creator-defends-his-game-as-a-game-5981097 | last = Good | work = Kotaku | publisher = Gawker Media | archive-date = 2021-03-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

